reviews.title: Beastly processor and a welcome upgrade
reviews.review: So first off the bat I just want to say that if you get this, get a different CPU cooler for it as well. The one that it comes with is terrible. I use a Noctua fan and it works great. For games it is an absolute beast and handles recording and rendering videos very well. Amazingly fast in both linux mint 20 and Windows 10. I upgraded from an old i7 3820 and this blows that out of the water.
